data.title: What to Do and See at Victoria Memorial: Timings, Activities and Events
data.meta_description: Victoria Memorial is a name shared by two famous monuments that were built in honour of Queen Victoria, the former ruler of the British Empire. One of them is located in Kolkata, India, and the other one is in London, England. Both of them are impressive examples of architecture and art that reflect the history and culture of their respective countries.
